Package: ggsn
Type: Package
Title: North symbols and scale bars for maps created with ggplot or ggmap
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.1),
    ggplot2
Imports:
    png,
    grid,
    maptools
Suggests:
    rgdal,
    ggmap
Description: Adds north symbols (18 options) and scale bars in kilometers to maps in geographic or metric coordinates created with ggplot or ggmap.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyLoad: yes
URL: https://github.com/oswaldosantos/ggsn
Authors@R: c(person(given='Oswaldo', family='Santos Baquero',
    email='oswaldosant@gmail.com', role=c("aut", "cre")))
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2015-08-21
